; Coverage test for post.cc
; Tests get_note with a transaction-level note.
; Note: the comment appears before the first posting, so ledger parses
; it as a transaction note, not a posting note; note merging is not tested.

2024/03/01 Groceries
    ; Post note here
    Expenses:Food     $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(note)\n"
 Post note here
 Post note here
end test
